<!--X-Body-of-Message-->
<pre>Hello.

We have decided to move our MLs (mailing lists) under a new subdomain
&quot;ml&quot; with SPF record.

Old address        : ML@xxxxxxxxxxxxxx
Old control address: ML-ctl@xxxxxxxxxxxxxx
New address        : ML@xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
New control address: ML-ctl@xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

Other parameters such as SMTP FROM or List-Id are also affected.

SPF records are configured so that mails from unauthorized
server will result in &quot;SoftFail&quot; at the moment, but we will eventually
change the configuration so that such mails shall result in &quot;Fail.&quot;

Regards,

-- 
YOSHIFUJI Hideaki @ USAGI Project  &lt;yoshfuji@xxxxxxxxxxxxxx&gt;
GPG-FP  : 9022 65EB 1ECF 3AD1 0BDF  80D8 4807 F894 E062 0EEA

</pre>
